            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Appio Iunio Silano <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Silio <lb n="2"/>Nerva co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Tillegus Ambati <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Susarrus <lb n="4"/>|(castello) Aiobrigiaeco hospitium <lb n="5"/>fecit cum Lougeis castellanis <lb n="6"/>Toletensibus sibi uxori libe<lb break="no" n="7"/>ris posterisque suis eumq<lb break="no" n="8"/>ue uxorem liberosque eius <lb n="9"/>in fidem clientelamque sua<lb break="no" n="10"/>m suorumque in perpetuo Cas<lb break="no" n="11"/>tellanei Toletensis receperunt <lb n="12"/>egit Tillegus Ambati ipse <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>istratibus</ex></expan> Latino Ari et Aio Temari
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tabula hospitalis.</p>
            </div>
